{"tid":748223,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"大家會點同外國人解釋廣東話嘅語氣","createTime":"2018-07-19T04:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T10:44:54.000Z","uid":175523,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"71f224ec187b6971c68ab865fdef8d3b736112b4","tid":748223,"uid":175523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:57:58.000Z","msg":"試過幾次有外國朋友問<br />\n點解廣東話孻尾成日搭住個la音<br />\n講到快個陣聽落去la la la咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我就諗住解釋個「啦」有咩用<br />\n所以用yes呢個比較簡單嘅字做例子<br />\n<br />\n係 = yes<br />\n係啦 = yes la&uarr;(I told you! You see?)<br />\n係喇 = yes la&darr;(Stop repeating, I know!)<br />\n係嘞 = yes lak  (開場白，諗唔到點譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n大部分人聽完都覺得個語氣系統幾複雜<br />\n咁我又多口舉多幾個例子<br />\n跟住就出事喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係嘅 = yes ge  (Got it)<br />\n係嘅～ = yes ge ~ (I see your point)<br />\n係㗎 = yes ga (Ya, it happens)<br />\n係㗎？ = yes ga? (You sure?)<br />\n係㗎喇 = yes gala (It cannot be changed)<br />\n<br />\n咁搭住個「係」當然可以試譯<br />\n但係如果搭其他嘢就要重新譯過<br />\n去到呢度大部分人應該都聽到萌出退意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗真啲仲有：<br />\n係啊<br />\n係呀(牙)？<br />\n係呢<br />\n係喎/噃<br />\n係啩<br />\n係囉/係囉(羅)<br />\n係咪？<br />\n<br />\n呢啲對我來講都係yes/yes?<br />\n只係感覺上有細微分別<br />\n而呢啲分別係我覺得好難表達<br />\n有時想同朋友表達呢啲意思<br />\n限於外語能力反而唔係太做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n甚至乎用蝗語有時都未必得<br />\n大家會點樣解釋呢啲字畀外國人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00801ae258b2251706cbc97463484f48a5c3b526","tid":748223,"uid":46835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:09:24.000Z","msg":"你研究開粵語架？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef5e18141785825d4515452387e7f91841ed657","tid":748223,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:10:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5ee64f86f50781cfa6bd3d1414a99201004e236","tid":748223,"uid":28759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:10:38.000Z","msg":"其實英文都係靠 intonation 做啫"},{"pid":"5aa4170629bad9b688ee277a660cb5d12d95d7e3","tid":748223,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ec75abc9c57ca237b36fa09622f8fc6916a294","tid":748223,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:11:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"30bbf8d73c0db63f495f3f23d4089c875586ab86","tid":748223,"uid":175523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00801ae258b2251706cbc97463484f48a5c3b526","tid":748223,"uid":46835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:09:24.000Z","msg":"你研究開粵語架？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:16:01.000Z","msg":"一竅不通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係有時同啲朋友會互相傾下自己母語"},{"pid":"93e8ba938ea1d8e6b36da6e47487d53ab0f87525","tid":748223,"uid":175523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ef5e18141785825d4515452387e7f91841ed657","tid":748223,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:10:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:20:29.000Z","msg":"除咗四其他真係得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5496f810471f750d9fe68b7354d1bd755b4ac075","tid":748223,"uid":175523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5ee64f86f50781cfa6bd3d1414a99201004e236","tid":748223,"uid":28759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:10:38.000Z","msg":"其實英文都係靠 intonation 做啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:23:32.000Z","msg":"英文嘅起伏係幫到表達個語氣<br />\n但係有時我想再細緻啲咁表現<br />\n就卡咗住咗，唔知點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa56b30b47bdf3a61c63caeecce6e173788a515e","tid":748223,"uid":72834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:32:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/粤语\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E7%B2%A4%E8%AF%AD&d=ffeL2UZe1D0zqWnfAH%2BT1aWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=4cb96ab9\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/粤语</a><br />\n語法有講"},{"pid":"1313f24c26103dba855dc447fbe3a6d651ec14e2","tid":748223,"uid":54871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:44:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}